author: julianfoad
msg: Fix the timing measurement of copying a repository, in the test suite. Also only
log that timing if 'log_with_timestamps' is true, following r1303737.
(copy_repos): Don't stop the clock until the commands have completed. Only
log the '<TIME = ...>' line if 'log_with_timestamps' is true.

author: scottbw
msg: Replaced methods deleted from 0.9.2 but added @deprecated tags to provide API-level backwards compatibility (see WOOKIE-330).

author: davidb
msg: Remove tag as artefacts to be released need to be re-signed.

author: julianfoad
msg: Make it easier to turn off timing information in the test suite, by
controlling it with a single boolean variable.  (There's no UI for this.)
(formatter): Use it to enable or disable the timestamp prefix on log lines.
(run_command_stdin): Use it to enable or disable the '<TIME = ...>' lines.
